 R‚ÜêTest_Stash_011(stopFlag batchFlag);‚éïTRAP;dir;rc;msg;buff
‚çù Executes StashShow with an explicit stash number
 ‚éïTRAP‚Üê(999 'C' '. ‚çù Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R‚ÜêT._Failed

 dir‚Üê‚àÜStashDir,'/SourceCode'
 'Create!'FilesAndDirs.CheckPath dir

 (‚äÇ'Hello')‚éïNPUT dir,'/file_1.txt'
 ‚àÜStashDir ##.APLGit2.Add''
 buff‚Üê##.APLGit2.StashPush ‚àÜStashDir
 ‚ÜíT.GoToTidyUp~‚à®/'Saved working directory and index state'‚ç∑‚àäbuff
 ‚éïMKDIR dir
 (‚äÇ'Hello2')‚éïNPUT dir,'/file_2.txt'
 ‚àÜStashDir ##.APLGit2.Add''
